I'D GET THROUGH D-DAY.

4
00:02:32,752 --> 00:02:35,155
LET ALONE THE NEXT PHASE
OR THE NEXT PHASE.

5
00:02:35,155 --> 00:02:37,857
I THOUGHT I WAS GOING TO
GET KILLED INSTANTLY.

6
00:02:37,857 --> 00:02:39,893
I THOUGHT ONE
OF TWO THINGS:

7
00:02:39,893 --> 00:02:42,191
A QUICK DEATH,
ER, OR...

8
