WITHOUT A SCRATCH.

9
00:02:44,998 --> 00:02:46,833
I THINK EVERYBODY
HAD FEAR.

10
00:02:46,833 --> 00:02:50,735
I THINK THERE'S PEOPLE
THAT CAN HANDLE FEAR.

11
00:02:52,038 --> 00:02:53,300
I THINK...

12
00:02:53,706 --> 00:02:56,042
I THINK I WAS
PROBABLY ONE OF THEM.

13
00:02:56,042 --> 00:02:57,577
I THINK I WAS
JUST AS...

14
00:02:57,577 --> 00:03:00,613
SCARED AS ANYBODY ELSE
EXCEPT I COULD THINK.

15
00:03:00,613 --> 00:03:04,743
IT'S A FEELING YOU WOULD
NOT LET YOURSELF DOWN,

16
00:03:05,251 --> 00:03:09,984
AND YOU WOULD NOT LET YOUR
CAMRADES OR YOUR UNIT DOWN.

17
00:03:10,323 --> 00:03:12,125
WE ALL HAD FEAR...

18
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:15,617
BUT WE ALL HAD
TRAINING TO KNOW THAT...

19
00:03:16,129 --> 00:03:18,498
YOU TRY TO HANDLE
YOUR FEAR

20
00:03:18,498 --> 00:03:20,667
AND WORK TO ACCOMPLISH

21
00:03:20,667 --> 00:03:23,693
WHAT YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BE DOING.

22
00:04:15,421 --> 00:04:18,618
HEY, IT LOOKS LIKE
WHAT'S-HIS-NAME.

23
00:04:19,525 --> 00:04:22,095
YOU KNOW,
FROM 1st PLATOON?

24
00:04:22,095 --> 00:04:23,926
OUR 1st PLATOON?

25
00:04:24,264 --> 00:04:25,754
