26
00:04:32,205 --> 00:04:33,229
BLITHE.

27
00:04:34,374 --> 00:04:35,807
HEY, BLITHE.

28
00:04:38,511 --> 00:04:39,603
BLITHE!

29
00:04:43,483 --> 00:04:44,814
( gunfire )

30
00:04:55,228 --> 00:04:57,287
THOUGHT THAT
WAS YOU.

31
00:04:59,932 --> 00:05:01,263
YOU ALONE?

32
00:05:03,803 --> 00:05:06,839
YOU'RE THE FIRST
FAMILIAR FACES I'VE SEEN.

33
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,907
I AIN'T SURPRISED.

34
00:05:07,907 --> 00:05:10,009
THEY DROPPED US
ALL OVER THE PENINSULA.

35
00:05:10,009 --> 00:05:15,003
WE'VE BEEN FIGHTING
WITH THE 502nd
SINCE WE HIT THE GROUND.

36
00:05:15,081 --> 00:05:15,945
YOU?

37
00:05:18,685 --> 00:05:20,448
OH, I'VE BEEN...

38
00:05:22,388 --> 00:05:24,447
