39
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:26,182
JOIN THE CLUB.

40
00:05:34,267 --> 00:05:35,598
( gunfire )

41
00:05:50,316 --> 00:05:51,184
HEY, FELLAS.

42
00:05:51,184 --> 00:05:54,620
WELL, LOOK WHO DECIDED
TO SHOW UP, FLOYD.

43
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,555
Hl THERE, LADZ.

44
00:05:55,555 --> 00:05:57,423
WE THOUGHT WE'D
NEVER FIND YOU GUYS.

45
00:05:57,423 --> 00:05:59,592
HEY, TAB,
GET A LOAD OF THIS.

46
00:05:59,592 --> 00:06:00,393
