YEAH, IT'S
THE REAL STUFF, MAN.

48
00:06:02,028 --> 00:06:03,791
YEAH, OF COURSE.

49
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:05,565
YOU LIKE THIS?

50
00:06:05,565 --> 00:06:06,199
OH, NICE.

51
00:06:06,199 --> 00:06:08,429
THAT'S A BEAUTY,
SARGE.

52
00:06:09,635 --> 00:06:14,163
MY LUGER'S GONNA PUT YOU
ALL TO SHAME WHEN I GET IT.

53
00:06:18,411 --> 00:06:20,379
HOW WAS YOUR JUMP?

54
