AH, MISSED THE DZ.

55
00:06:22,548 --> 00:06:24,450
YEAH, THAT GOES
WITHOUT SAYING.

56
00:06:24,450 --> 00:06:25,781
I GUESS SO.

57
00:06:25,985 --> 00:06:28,054
GOT ANY SOUVENIRS
TO TRADE?

58
00:06:28,054 --> 00:06:28,918
HUH?

59
00:06:30,857 --> 00:06:31,758
THEY'RE ALL TICKIN'.

60
00:06:31,758 --> 00:06:34,193
UNLIKE THEIR
PREVIOUS OWNERS.

61
00:06:34,193 --> 00:06:35,561
GOT ANYTHING GOOD?

62
00:06:35,561 --> 00:06:36,653
NOT YET.

63
00:06:37,530 --> 00:06:38,326
HEY.

64
00:06:44,203 --> 00:06:46,372
SO, HAVE
WE LOST ANYBODY?

65
00:06:46,372 --> 00:06:48,708
TOMMY BURGESS
TOOK ONE IN THE FACE.

66
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:51,344
POPEYE WYNN GOT
PINCHED IN THE BEHIND.

67
00:06:51,344 --> 00:06:53,246
BUT THEY'RE
GONNA BE OKAY.

68
00:06:53,246 --> 00:06:54,213
THAT'S GOOD.

69
00:06:54,213 --> 00:06:57,116
YOU RUN INTO LIEUTENANT MEEHAN
IN YOUR TRAVELS?

70
00:06:57,116 --> 00:06:58,217
NO, WHY?

71
00:06:58,217 --> 00:06:59,919
COMPANY HQ'S
STILL MISSING.

72
00:06:59,919 --> 00:07:02,021
THEY THINK THE PLANE
WENT DOWN.

73
00:07:02,021 --> 00:07:03,289
THEY SAY
HE'S GONNA TURN UP.

74
00:07:03,289 --> 00:07:05,491
YEAH, I AIN'T
HOLDING MY BREATH.

75
00:07:05,491 --> 00:07:07,789
WHO'S IN COMMAND,
THEN?

76
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:08,895
WINTERS FOR NOW.

77
00:07:08,895 --> 00:07:11,764
LIEUTENANT WELSH
IS 1st PLATOON.

78
00:07:11,764 --> 00:07:14,631
