LET'S GO,
1st PLATOON!

79
00:07:18,771 --> 00:07:20,740
EASY'S MOVING OUT!

80
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:22,230
ON YOUR FEET.

81
00:07:23,876 --> 00:07:25,844
STAND UP, LET'S GO.

82
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:28,911
