DISCIPLINE FROM HERE ON.

85
00:07:32,552 --> 00:07:34,153
NO TALKING,
NO SMOKING.

86
00:07:34,153 --> 00:07:37,323
AND NO PLAYING GRAB-FANNY WITH
THE MAN IN FRONT OF YOU, LADS.

87
00:07:37,323 --> 00:07:38,891
