CARENTAN.

89
00:07:40,693 --> 00:07:41,527
THAT SOUNDS LIKE FUN.

90
00:07:41,527 --> 00:07:44,230
IT'S THE ONLY PLACE
WHERE ARMOR FROM OMAHA
AND UTAH BEACH

91
00:07:44,230 --> 00:07:45,364
CAN LINK UP
AND HEAD INLAND.

92
00:07:45,364 --> 00:07:48,000
UNTIL WE TAKE CARENTAN,
THEY'RE STUCK IN THE SAND.

93
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:51,170
GENERAL TAYLOR'S SENDING
THE WHOLE DIVISION.

94
00:07:51,170 --> 00:07:51,904
REMEMBER, BOYS...

95
00:07:51,904 --> 00:07:55,708
GIVE ME THREE DAYS AND
THREE NIGHTS OF HARD FIGHTING

96
00:07:55,708 --> 00:07:58,074
AND YOU WILL
BE RELIEVED.

97
00:07:58,478 --> 00:07:59,545
LIEUTENANT.

98
00:07:59,545 --> 00:08:00,913
LIEUTENANT,
I'LL TAKE POINT.

99
00:08:00,913 --> 00:08:03,649
CORPORAL HOOBLER
WILL BE LEAD SCOUT.

100
00:08:03,649 --> 00:08:06,052
BLITHE, GLAD YOU
COULD JOIN US.

101
00:08:06,052 --> 00:08:06,819
THANK YOU, SIR.

102
00:08:06,819 --> 00:08:09,121
1st PLATOON, FALL IN
BEHIND FOX COMPANY.

103
00:08:09,121 --> 00:08:12,658
YOU PEOPLE FROM 2nd
AND 3rd PLATOON, FOLLOW US.

104
00:08:12,658 --> 00:08:14,558
LET'S SHAKE A LEG.

105
00:08:15,061 --> 00:08:17,363
ANOTHER THING
TO REMEMBER, BOYS...

106
00:08:17,363 --> 00:08:19,490
FLIES SPREAD DISEASE.

107
00:08:19,832 --> 00:08:22,062
SO, KEEP YOURS CLOSED.

108
00:08:22,401 --> 00:08:23,834
( laughing )

109
00:09:08,748 --> 00:09:10,545
DON'T WAKE JERRY.

110
