DAMN!

111
00:09:29,969 --> 00:09:30,670
WHAT?

112
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:33,072
WE LOST
"F" COMPANY, SIR.

113
00:09:33,072 --> 00:09:34,096
AGAIN?

114
00:09:36,042 --> 00:09:37,777
WE LOST
"F" COMPANY.

115
00:09:37,777 --> 00:09:38,678
AGAIN?

116
