PERCONTE, GO BACK AND PASS
THE WORD TO HOLD UP.

118
00:09:42,648 --> 00:09:43,282
YES, SIR.

119
00:09:43,282 --> 00:09:45,084
HOOBLER, TAKE BLITHE,
GO FIND "F" COMPANY.

120
00:09:45,084 --> 00:09:45,885
YES, SIR.

121
00:09:45,885 --> 00:09:46,909
BLITHE.

122
00:09:59,432 --> 00:10:00,296
SHIT.

123
00:10:05,671 --> 00:10:06,439
