YEAH, I GOT HOOBLER
AND BLITHE OUT THERE NOW.

125
00:10:08,374 --> 00:10:09,175
WHY HAVE
WE STOPPED?

126
00:10:09,175 --> 00:10:13,980
THIS IS ABOUT OFFICERS
CRAPPING OUT IN
THEIR TRAINING, NIX.

127
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:17,643
COME ON, LET'S GET
THIS SHOW ON THE ROAD.

128
00:10:21,587 --> 00:10:23,316
DANG MISQUITOES.

129
00:10:35,067 --> 00:10:36,500
WHAT IS IT?

130
00:10:36,669 --> 00:10:37,465
SHH.

131
00:10:40,339 --> 00:10:41,306
FLASH.

132
00:10:41,607 --> 00:10:42,699
THUNDER.

133
00:10:45,611 --> 00:10:48,681
I CAN HEAR Y'ALL ALL THE WAY
ACROSS THE FIELD.

134
00:10:48,681 --> 00:10:50,512
YOU "F" COMPANY?

135
00:10:51,083 --> 00:10:52,573
THAT'S RIGHT.

136
00:10:55,321 --> 00:10:57,223
WHERE Y'ALL BEEN?

137
00:10:57,223 --> 00:10:59,191
BLITHE, GO BACK
TO THE LIEUTENANT.

138
00:10:59,191 --> 00:11:00,793
TELL HIM WE'VE
FOUND "F" COMPANY.

139
00:11:00,793 --> 00:11:03,696
I'LL FIGURE OUT WHERE
THESE YOKELS ARE AT.

140
00:11:03,696 --> 00:11:06,631
