PRIVATE.

142
00:11:20,613 --> 00:11:22,715
DID YOU FIND
FOX COMPANY?

143
00:11:22,715 --> 00:11:23,909
YES, SIR.

144
00:11:25,951 --> 00:11:27,586
I THOUGHT HE...

145
00:11:27,586 --> 00:11:29,554
