STRAIGHT UP THE MIDDLE,

157
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:17,536
HARD AND FAST.

158
00:12:17,536 --> 00:12:18,537
WE HAVE TO
MOVE QUICKLY.

159
00:12:18,537 --> 00:12:22,303
I'LL BE RIGHT BEHIND YOU
WITH 2nd AND 3rd.

160
00:12:35,654 --> 00:12:36,188
GO!

161
00:12:36,188 --> 00:12:38,486
LET'S GO, 1st,
LET'S GO.

162
00:12:40,392 --> 00:12:41,791
GO, GO, GO!

163
00:12:51,704 --> 00:12:52,872
IN THE DITCH!

164
00:12:52,872 --> 00:12:54,134
INCOMING!

165
00:12:59,845 --> 00:13:00,646
GODDAMN IT!

166
00:13:00,646 --> 00:13:02,915
