175
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:23,335
FOLLOW ME, EASY!

176
00:13:23,335 --> 00:13:24,597
MOVE OUT!

177
00:13:24,703 --> 00:13:26,364
MOVE OUT, MEN!

178
00:13:26,672 --> 00:13:27,468
GO!

179
00:13:29,308 --> 00:13:31,299
