OKAY, I'M OUT.

196
00:15:12,144 --> 00:15:13,076
SHIT!

197
00:15:16,048 --> 00:15:19,779
GUARNERE, CLEAR THAT
SECTOR ON THE RIGHT!

198
00:15:22,621 --> 00:15:23,815
WITH ME!

199
00:15:30,996 --> 00:15:32,827
YOU OKAY,
SHIFTY?

200
00:15:34,466 --> 00:15:37,264
WE GOTTA TAKE
THAT WAREHOUSE!

201
00:15:39,305 --> 00:15:40,397
SHIFTY!

202
00:15:43,609 --> 00:15:45,736
HAMMER THESE WINDOWS.

203
00:15:48,614 --> 00:15:52,217
TIPPER, TAKE LIEBGOTT, START
CLEARING THESE BUILDINGS.

204
00:15:52,217 --> 00:15:53,184
RIGHT.

205
00:15:54,753 --> 00:15:56,744
